CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "Carnegie Tech Graduates - Five Negroes received degrees at ceremonies at Carnegie Institute of Technology last Thursday...T. Strothers, 104 Chalfont Street, was graduated at...[bache]lor of Fine Arts in Sculpture. The Courier wishes the [gradu]ates of Carnegie Tech the best of luck in their [vo]cations."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Carnegie Institute of Technology graduate T. Strothers, standing with other graduates in Syria Mosque, Oakland
